Bafana Bafana coach Hugo Broos has asked for a little bit of patience in building a world-conquering team. Tshepo Thobane has more. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Newly-appointed Bafana Bafana coach Hugo Broos has committed life and limb to ensure the success of Bafana Bafana. The Belgian has outlined his plans to see Bafana Bafana return to their glory days by qualifying for AFCON and the FIFA World Cup. However, he’s asked for a little bit of patience in building a world-conquering team. WATCH: Hugo Broos on his plans for Bafana Bafana The Belgian has promised to give youngsters a chance in the national team. Broos has pledged to include a South African coach as part of his technical team and will be in constant contact with Premiership coaches for further inputs.